{"tid":749381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打籃球被犯規　美國男子堅持報警","createTime":"2018-07-20T03:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T09:41:27.000Z","uid":122,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2370d3edb0b028e7527c2be90a32ba8c1ae95acc","tid":749381,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:45:31.000Z","msg":"美國維吉尼亞州一名男子在健身室打籃球時，不滿被他人犯規推倒地上，生氣地跑到櫃檯要求職員報警。目擊者把警察到場情況拍下，影片放上網後爆紅，獲得9萬多個讚好及3萬多次轉發。<br />\n <br />\n目擊者鮑伊（Marcellus Bowie）說，兩名男子先發生小爭執，一名男子上籃投失後，防守時刻意地撞向為隊友單擋掩護的球員，把對方撞倒到地上，「他的手有點打到他的臉。我不認為他有意打他，像是無意間推倒了對手。」<br />\n <br />\n「那個人站起來說，『我要報警！』。所有人四處張望，覺得困惑。他氣呼呼地走出球場。我個人以為他在開玩笑，但過頭了。」及後，員警真的到場，所有人都覺得難以置信。<br />\n <br />\nTwitter用戶@_togs發佈警察到場調查的相片，附註：「今天是我人生中第一次，經歷有人因為打籃球被嚴重犯規而報警。」他說：「我們很疑惑，完全糊塗，我還在糊塗。我不知道為甚麼，或是他覺得警員可以做甚麼。並不是說他一拳打他臉，或把他摔到地上，這只是籃球遊戲。」<br />\n <br />\n拍下影片放上Instagram的穆拉巴（Thomas Mulabah）說：「在籃球史上，這從來未發生過。」他拍片問其他球員，「你被犯規會報警嗎？」又把鏡頭轉向負責調查的警員，「你試過因為籃球犯規被召來嗎？」警員回答：「沒。這是我第一次（處理）籃球犯規。」<br />\n <br />\n勞登縣（Loudoun County）警方確認，警員周一下午接報指斯特靈（Sterling）的LA Fitness健身室，有一名球員襲擊另一人，下午6時42分派員到場調查。<br />\n <br />\n負責調查的警員肯尼迪（Josiah Kennedy）在筆記上寫道，兩名未公開全名的球員「承認他們在打籃球時對彼此犯規」，「我提出報案，但他們兩人都不想。管理人員再給他們一次機會，叫他們要玩得有禮，否則他們二人當天都會被趕出健身室。」（北美中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"f9810ec0256b888dcfd7899b4a7c67f31f2129b4","tid":749381,"uid":109983,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"這只是籃球遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bbe13c5396ca10fa4222022e68fe9c881d78ab","tid":749381,"uid":61832,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"f9810ec0256b888dcfd7899b4a7c67f31f2129b4","tid":749381,"uid":109983,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"這只是籃球遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"玩具"},{"pid":"ebfb4e543513c5f2471312802d33681d4e7ae2ce","tid":749381,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"玩具撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf397a3d8ff1d7f21687a90c2ef0711da3fa7b7","tid":749381,"uid":45518,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"認真玩玩具"},{"pid":"93570e05cea5e9fec51a0926fa53aece94b28167","tid":749381,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f9810ec0256b888dcfd7899b4a7c67f31f2129b4","tid":749381,"uid":109983,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"這只是籃球遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:31:42.000Z","msg":"It's just a basketball game，的翻譯離晒大譜"},{"pid":"7c762a2f684dcfdbbf4eb4b2fbd1f424ca3a8e84","tid":749381,"uid":113626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"香港果d仲仆街, 踢到你前十字斷埋報警都無用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e74f365e7334cd67593744e18b2b740422f22d0","tid":749381,"uid":41760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"bcd8d543fc04730d882ca7884fc5abc686de57d3","tid":749381,"uid":194630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:37:19.000Z","msg":"小器鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707fb376e0eb5b45d722e58dbc10bcc58cb027f0","tid":749381,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:39:47.000Z","msg":"響健身室打籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj